<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 02:14:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军加大对加沙的打击力度并准备地面入侵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-ramps-up-strikes-on-gaza-prepares-for-ground-invasion/0000018b-1b4c-d2fc-a59f-db5d8aee0000</link><description>在战争的第四天，在南部社区发现了 30 名失踪的以色列人；军队已通知50名俘虏的家属，死亡人数已达900人；拜登全力支持以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 01:46:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-ramps-up-strikes-on-gaza-prepares-for-ground-invasion/0000018b-1b4c-d2fc-a59f-db5d8aee0000</guid></item><item><title>塔克·卡尔森质疑美国对以色列战争的支持——共和党会效仿吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/tucker-carlson-questions-u-s-support-for-israel-war-could-the-gop-follow/0000018b-19c2-dcc0-a3df-9de2ad700000</link><description>卡尔森反对共和党支持以色列对哈马斯进行自卫反击，这使他成为一个异类。但他巨大的影响力可能会让一些共和党人对以色列持更加怀疑的立场</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 23:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-11/ty-article/.premium/tucker-carlson-questions-u-s-support-for-israel-war-could-the-gop-follow/0000018b-19c2-dcc0-a3df-9de2ad700000</guid></item><item><title>哈佛大学学生支持的指责以色列暴力的声明引发强烈反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/statement-blaming-israel-for-violence-endorsed-by-harvard-students-unleashes-backlash/0000018b-1a43-d465-abbb-1ef795fc0000</link><description>哈佛大学数十个学生组织签署的一份声明，被认为使哈马斯屠杀近千名以色列人合法化，在这所常春藤盟校引发轩然大波</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 20:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/statement-blaming-israel-for-violence-endorsed-by-harvard-students-unleashes-backlash/0000018b-1a43-d465-abbb-1ef795fc0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：美国支持以色列对哈马斯“纯粹、纯粹的邪恶”做出“迅速、果断、压倒性”的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-u-s-supports-israeli-overwhelming-response-against-hamas-pure-evil/0000018b-1af4-d08b-adef-1ff6dda30000</link><description>拜登说，这次袭击呼应了“千年来的反犹太主义和对犹太人的种族灭绝”，并重申美国“与以色列站在一起”。他还警告任何考虑利用这种情况的国家或组织：“不要这样做。”不&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 19:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-u-s-supports-israeli-overwhelming-response-against-hamas-pure-evil/0000018b-1af4-d08b-adef-1ff6dda30000</guid></item><item><title>“所以全世界都知道发生了什么”：卡法阿扎基布兹的屠杀现场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/so-the-world-knows-what-happened-the-scene-of-slaughter-at-kibbutz-kfar-azza/0000018b-1aa1-df31-a99f-7fe3eae50000</link><description>800 名以色列人居住在卡法阿扎 (Kfar Azza)，这是加沙城可见范围内的一个基布兹。现在，他们中的许多人都只是数字：死亡、受伤、失踪、被俘。参观大屠杀以来最大的犹太人屠杀现场</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 19:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/so-the-world-knows-what-happened-the-scene-of-slaughter-at-kibbutz-kfar-azza/0000018b-1aa1-df31-a99f-7fe3eae50000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙边境附近的以色列基布兹躲避恐怖分子的三十名失踪者获救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/thirty-missing-who-hid-from-terrorists-at-israeli-kibbutz-are-rescued/0000018b-1aae-d2fc-a59f-dbbfc0290000</link><description>周六大批来自加沙的哈马斯恐怖分子入侵后，这 16 名以色列人和 14 名泰国人躲藏起来，周一晚间警方收到有关他们下落的信息后获救。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 18:41:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/thirty-missing-who-hid-from-terrorists-at-israeli-kibbutz-are-rescued/0000018b-1aae-d2fc-a59f-dbbfc0290000</guid></item><item><title>392名美国众议院议员提出支持以色列对抗哈马斯“野蛮”袭击的决议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/392-u-s-house-reps-back-israel-against-barbaric-hamas-attacks/0000018b-1aa7-dcc0-a3df-9ea778210000</link><description>广泛的支持，只有 43 名众议院议员作为最初的共同提案国缺失，反映出两党对以色列的支持几乎是史无前例的，而此时华盛顿也许从未陷入过这样的政治僵局</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 18:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/392-u-s-house-reps-back-israel-against-barbaric-hamas-attacks/0000018b-1aa7-dcc0-a3df-9ea778210000</guid></item><item><title>在埃隆·马斯克的帮助下，有关以色列和加沙的虚假信息困扰着社交媒体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/disinfo-on-israel-gaza-plagues-social-media-with-elon-musks-aid/0000018b-1a84-dcc0-a3df-9ea425840000</link><description>几周前，马斯克在一次 X 活动中与著名的右翼犹太人物一起放大了反犹太阴谋论，并为自己反犹太主义的指控进行了辩护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 17:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/disinfo-on-israel-gaza-plagues-social-media-with-elon-musks-aid/0000018b-1a84-dcc0-a3df-9ea425840000</guid></item><item><title>基布兹被毁：我从未想过我会为我的家写一首挽歌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/i-never-imagined-id-write-an-elegy-for-my-kibbutz/0000018b-1a1f-d2fc-a59f-db1f5ff70000</link><description>这不仅仅是一首关于加沙边境附近尼尔奥兹基布兹的数十人死亡和失踪的挽歌，也不仅仅是关于一个被摧毁的社区的挽歌。这是对国家的哀叹</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/i-never-imagined-id-write-an-elegy-for-my-kibbutz/0000018b-1a1f-d2fc-a59f-db1f5ff70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军轰炸加沙地带 至少770人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/at-least-770-dead-as-the-israel-air-force-bombs-the-gaza-strip/0000018b-1a53-df31-a99f-7fd3bd1e0000</link><description>加沙地带居民表示，这是自周六战争爆发以来最严厉的空袭，联合国报告称，由于基础设施遭到破坏，40万加沙人缺乏自来水</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 16:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/at-least-770-dead-as-the-israel-air-force-bombs-the-gaza-strip/0000018b-1a53-df31-a99f-7fd3bd1e0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯囚禁的美国公民家属说：“拜登，这也是你的责任”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-its-your-responsibility-too-say-families-of-u-s-citizens-in-hamas-captivity/0000018b-1a22-dcc0-a3df-9e2264520000</link><description>失踪或被哈马斯绑架的美国公民的家人希望美国将被俘的以色列国防军士兵视为“根据国际法的战俘”。他们还引用了以色列和美国政府迄今为止没有发布的任何信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-its-your-responsibility-too-say-families-of-u-s-citizens-in-hamas-captivity/0000018b-1a22-dcc0-a3df-9e2264520000</guid></item><item><title>Telegram 和 Twitter 如何击败电视报道哈马斯与以色列的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-telegram-and-twitter-beat-television-to-cover-the-hamas-israel-war-as-it-happened/0000018b-189c-df31-a99f-7ddfc7570000</link><description>在以色列人得知他们受到攻击一小时后，很明显这个消息一无所知。他们在电视上报道了以色列中部的警报以及哈马斯武装分子从加沙越境的报道。报告？在社交媒体上我已经看到他们开着吉普车四处游荡</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-telegram-and-twitter-beat-television-to-cover-the-hamas-israel-war-as-it-happened/0000018b-189c-df31-a99f-7ddfc7570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军高级军官：“是我和我的三四个人对抗数十名哈马斯战士”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/it-was-me-and-3-or-4-of-my-men-against-dozens-of-hamas-fighters-at-every-encounter/0000018b-1970-dcc0-a3df-9d700b0c0000</link><description>一名师指挥官在回忆哈马斯入侵的最初几个小时时说，他的士兵受到了沉重打击，没有人看到大局，并承认“我们将不得不面对关于我们如何运作的严峻问题”</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/it-was-me-and-3-or-4-of-my-men-against-dozens-of-hamas-fighters-at-every-encounter/0000018b-1970-dcc0-a3df-9d700b0c0000</guid></item><item><title>我儿子从星期六起就失踪了。大神请给我答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article-opinion/my-son-has-been-missing-since-saturday-god-please-give-me-answers/0000018b-1959-d2fc-a59f-d959a60c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 15:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article-opinion/my-son-has-been-missing-since-saturday-god-please-give-me-answers/0000018b-1959-d2fc-a59f-d959a60c0000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯火箭弹和铁穹顶下，以色列英语社区震惊地哀悼阵亡士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/amid-hamas-rockets-israels-stunned-english-speaking-community-mourns-fallen-soldiers/0000018b-1998-df31-a99f-7ddbe6d60000</link><description>随着哈马斯继续发射数十枚火箭弹，数百名哀悼者聚集在军事公墓，参加以色列英语国家移民阵亡士兵的葬礼</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 14:45:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/amid-hamas-rockets-israels-stunned-english-speaking-community-mourns-fallen-soldiers/0000018b-1998-df31-a99f-7ddbe6d60000</guid></item><item><title>紧急简报：加入《国土报》关于以色列-加沙战争的现场简报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/zoom-events/2023-10-10/ty-article/.highlight/emergency-briefing-join-haaretzs-live-briefing-on-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-19f4-d465-abbb-1df66fa90000</link><description>立即注册，参加 10 月 11 日星期三由国土报顶级专家举办的仅限订阅者的 Zoom 简报</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 14:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/zoom-events/2023-10-10/ty-article/.highlight/emergency-briefing-join-haaretzs-live-briefing-on-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-19f4-d465-abbb-1df66fa90000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列人逃离被围困的加沙边境城镇，抗议者转向救援工作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-israelis-flee-besieged-gaza-border-towns-protesters-pivot-to-relief-work/0000018b-1925-dcc0-a3df-9d259f1f0000</link><description>像Bonot Alternativa和Brothers and Sisters in Arms这样的团体花了一年时间与内塔尼亚胡政府削弱司法机构的企图作斗争。现在他们正在帮助逃离哈马斯袭击的以色列人</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 13:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-israelis-flee-besieged-gaza-border-towns-protesters-pivot-to-relief-work/0000018b-1925-dcc0-a3df-9d259f1f0000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团表示，以色列联盟领导人委托内塔尼亚胡组建联合政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-coalition-heads-entrust-netanyahu-with-forming-unity-govt-likud-says/0000018b-196b-dcc0-a3df-9d6b70780000</link><description>联盟领导人讨论了民族团结党的提议，该提议的条件是组建精简的战时内阁，排除极右翼部长本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇。本格维尔办公室在一份声明中表示，战时内阁的组建反映了“小政治”</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 12:44:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-coalition-heads-entrust-netanyahu-with-forming-unity-govt-likud-says/0000018b-196b-dcc0-a3df-9d6b70780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部哈马斯大屠杀后，基布兹人口死亡 10%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/10-percent-of-kibbutz-population-found-dead-after-hamas-massacre-in-southern-israel/0000018b-191c-df31-a99f-7ddf54fa0000</link><description>救援组织表示，在哈马斯武装分子通过陆路、空中和海上进入以色列、杀害边境社区平民并将他人劫持为人质两天后，在贝埃里基布兹发现了 108 具以色列人的尸体</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 11:24:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/.premium/10-percent-of-kibbutz-population-found-dead-after-hamas-massacre-in-southern-israel/0000018b-191c-df31-a99f-7ddf54fa0000</guid></item><item><title>网络明星纳斯日报：我认为自己是巴勒斯坦以色列人，现在我首先是以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/internet-star-nas-daily-i-identified-as-palestinian-israeli-now-im-firstly-israeli/0000018b-190b-d2fc-a59f-d91b94240000</link><description>记录他的世界旅行的在线社区“纳斯日报”的创始人努塞尔·亚辛向他的数百万粉丝表示，他在加沙-以色列战争期间支持以色列，并且“不想生活在巴勒斯坦政府的统治下”</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Oct 2023 11:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-10/ty-article/internet-star-nas-daily-i-identified-as-palestinian-israeli-now-im-firstly-israeli/0000018b-190b-d2fc-a59f-d91b94240000</guid></item></channel></rss>